ref=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die Eigenschaft <strong><code>Number.EPSILON</code></strong> beschreibt den Unterschied zwischen 1 und der kleinsten Gleitpunktzahl größer als 1.</p>\n\n<p>Man muss kein Objekt von Typ <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a>&nbsp; erzeugen, um auf diese statische Eigenschaft zuzugreifen. Man muss nur <code>Number.EPSILON</code> aufrufen.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/number-epsilon.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"><table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"header\" colspan=\"2\">Eigenschaftsattribute von <code>Number.EPSILON</code></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Schreibbar</td>\n      <td>nein</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Aufzählbar</td>\n      <td>nein</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Konfigurierbar</td>\n      <td>nein</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die <code>EPSILON</code> Eigenschaft hat einen ungefähren Wert von <code>2.2204460492503130808472633361816E-16</code> order <code>2<sup>-52</sup></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"testgleichung","title":"Testgleichung","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ny <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nz <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nequal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">abs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> z<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">EPSILON</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js line-numbers  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">EPSILON</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">EPSILON</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">52</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-number.epsilon\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.EPSILON' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-number.epsilon\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.EPSILON' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Number.EPSILON","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/EPSILON/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Nu